msgid ""
"``backend``: Storage backend -- one of ``POSIX``, ``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, "
"``HF3FS``, ``OBJ``, ``AZURE_BLOB``."
msgstr ""
"``backend``: 存储后端 -- 其中之一为 ``POSIX``, ``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, ``HF3FS``, "
"``OBJ``, ``AZURE_BLOB``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:50
msgid ""
"``pool_size``: Number of storage descriptors to pre-allocate (must be > "
"0)."
msgstr "``pool_size``: 预分配的存储描述符数量（必须大于 0）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:52 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:125
msgid "**Backend-specific parameters (``backend_params``):**"
msgstr "**后端特定参数 (``backend_params``):**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:54
msgid "File-based backends (``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, ``POSIX``, ``HF3FS``) require:"
msgstr "基于文件的后端（``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, ``POSIX``, ``HF3FS``）需要："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:56
msgid "``file_path``: Directory path for storing L2 data."
msgstr "``file_path``: 存储 L2 数据的目录路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:57
msgid ""
"``use_direct_io``: ``\"true\"`` or ``\"false\"`` -- whether to use direct"
" I/O."
msgstr "``use_direct_io``: ``\"true\"`` 或 ``\"false\"`` -- 是否使用直接 I/O。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:59
msgid ""
"The ``OBJ`` and ``AZURE_BLOB`` backends (object stores) do not require "
"``file_path``."
msgstr "``OBJ`` 和 ``AZURE_BLOB`` 后端（对象存储）不需要 ``file_path``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:61
msgid "**Backend descriptions:**"
msgstr "**后端描述：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:67
msgid "Backend"
msgstr "后端"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:68 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:753
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:807 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:847
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:69
msgid "``POSIX``"
msgstr "``POSIX``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:70
msgid "Standard POSIX file I/O.  Works on any file system.  No direct I/O."
msgstr "标准的 POSIX 文件 I/O。适用于任何文件系统。无直接 I/O。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:71
msgid "``GDS``"
msgstr "``GDS``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:72
msgid ""
"NVIDIA GPU Direct Storage.  Enables direct GPU-to-storage transfers "
"bypassing the CPU.  Requires NVMe SSDs with GDS support."
msgstr "NVIDIA GPU 直接存储。支持直接的 GPU 到存储的传输，绕过 CPU。需要支持 GDS 的 NVMe SSD。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:74
msgid "``GDS_MT``"
msgstr "``GDS_MT``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:75
msgid "Multi-threaded variant of GDS for higher throughput."
msgstr "GDS 的多线程变体，以提高吞吐量。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:76
msgid "``HF3FS``"
msgstr "``HF3FS``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:77
msgid "Shared file system backend (e.g., for distributed/networked storage)."
msgstr "共享文件系统后端（例如，用于分布式/网络存储）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:78
msgid "``OBJ``"
msgstr "``OBJ``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:79
msgid "Object store backend.  No local file path required."
msgstr "对象存储后端。无需本地文件路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:80
msgid "``AZURE_BLOB``"
msgstr "``AZURE_BLOB``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:81
msgid "Object store backend for Azure Blob Storage.  No local file path required."
msgstr "Azure Blob Storage 的对象存储后端。无需本地文件路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:83 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:142
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:185 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:357
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:445 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:601
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:654
msgid "**Configuration examples:**"
msgstr "**配置示例：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:106
msgid "``nixl_store_dynamic`` -- NIXL-based dynamic storage with persist/recover"
msgstr "``nixl_store_dynamic`` -- 基于 NIXL 的动态存储，具有持久化/恢复功能"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:108
msgid ""
"A dynamic variant of the NIXL adapter that opens and registers files per-"
"operation instead of pre-allocating them at init. This enables:"
msgstr "NIXL 适配器的动态变体，根据操作打开和注册文件，而不是在初始化时预分配。这使得："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:111
msgid "**Persist/recover** -- cached KV metadata survives restarts."
msgstr "**持久化/恢复** -- 缓存的 KV 元数据在重启后依然存在。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:112
msgid ""
"**No fd limits** -- files are opened and closed per transfer, so the "
"cache can grow beyond OS open-file-descriptor limits."
msgstr "**无文件描述符限制** -- 文件在每次传输时打开和关闭，因此缓存可以超出操作系统的打开文件描述符限制。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:117
msgid ""
"Only file-based backends are supported (``POSIX``, ``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, "
"``HF3FS``). The ``OBJ`` and ``AZURE_BLOB`` backends are not supported "
"yet."
msgstr ""
"仅支持基于文件的后端（``POSIX``, ``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, ``HF3FS``）。``OBJ`` 和 "
"``AZURE_BLOB`` 后端尚不支持。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:122
msgid ""
"``backend``: Storage backend -- one of ``POSIX``, ``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, "
"``HF3FS``."
msgstr "``backend``: 存储后端 -- 其中之一为 ``POSIX``, ``GDS``, ``GDS_MT``, ``HF3FS``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:127
msgid "``file_path``: Directory path for storing L2 data files."
msgstr "``file_path``: 存储 L2 数据文件的目录路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:128
msgid "``use_direct_io``: ``\"true\"`` or ``\"false\"``."
msgstr "``use_direct_io``: ``\"true\"`` 或 ``\"false\"``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:129
msgid ""
"``max_capacity_gb``: Maximum storage capacity in GB. The adapter rejects "
"stores when this limit is reached. Required for the eviction controller "
"to compute usage."
msgstr ""
"``max_capacity_gb``: 最大存储容量（以 GB "
"为单位）。当达到此限制时，适配器会拒绝存储。此项对于逐出控制器计算使用情况是必需的。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:133
msgid "**Optional fields (for persist):**"
msgstr "**可选字段（用于持久化）：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:135
msgid ""
"``persist_enabled`` (bool, default ``true``): If ``true``, data files are"
" kept on disk at shutdown. If ``false``, all data files are deleted on "
"shutdown."
msgstr ""
"``persist_enabled`` (bool, 默认 ``true``): 如果 ``true``，数据文件将在关闭时保留在磁盘上。如果 "
"``false``，所有数据文件将在关闭时被删除。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:139
msgid ""
"Lookup always checks secondary storage (disk) on miss and lazily "
"populates the in-memory index when a file is found."
msgstr "查找总是在未命中时检查二级存储（磁盘），并在找到文件时懒惰地填充内存中的索引。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:155
msgid "**Persist / secondary lookup behaviour:**"
msgstr "**持久化 / 次级查找行为:**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:157
msgid ""
"On **shutdown**, the adapter keeps data files on disk by default "
"(``persist_enabled`` defaults to ``true``). If explicitly set to "
"``false``, all data files are deleted to avoid orphaned storage."
msgstr ""
"在 **关闭** 时，适配器默认将数据文件保留在磁盘上（``persist_enabled`` 默认为 ``true``）。如果明确设置为 "
"``false``，则所有数据文件将被删除，以避免孤立存储。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:160
msgid ""
"On **startup**, the in-memory index is empty. Every lookup miss falls "
"through to a secondary lookup on disk: if the deterministic file exists, "
"it is treated as a hit and the in-memory index is populated lazily from "
"the file size."
msgstr ""
"在 **启动** "
"时，内存中的索引是空的。每次查找未命中都会转到磁盘上的二次查找：如果确定性文件存在，则将其视为命中，并根据文件大小懒惰地填充内存中的索引。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:166
msgid "``fs`` -- File-system backed storage"
msgstr "``fs`` -- 文件系统支持的存储"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:168
msgid ""
"A pure file-system L2 adapter using async I/O (``aiofiles``).  Each KV "
"cache object is stored as a raw ``.data`` file whose name encodes the "
"full ``ObjectKey``.  Does **not** require NIXL -- works on any POSIX file"
" system."
msgstr ""
"一个纯文件系统的 L2 适配器，使用异步 I/O (``aiofiles``)。每个 KV Cache 对象作为一个原始的 ``.data`` "
"文件存储，其名称编码了完整的 ``ObjectKey``。**不**需要 NIXL -- 可以在任何 POSIX 文件系统上工作。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:174 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:311
msgid "``base_path``: Directory for storing KV cache files."
msgstr "``base_path``: 存储 KV Cache 文件的目录。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:176 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:225
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:313 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:397
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:586 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:638
msgid "**Optional fields:**"
msgstr "**可选字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:178
msgid ""
"``relative_tmp_dir``: Relative sub-directory for temporary files during "
"writes (atomic rename on completion)."
msgstr "``relative_tmp_dir``: 写入期间临时文件的相对子目录（完成时进行原子重命名）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:180
msgid ""
"``read_ahead_size``: Trigger file-system read-ahead by reading this many "
"bytes first (positive integer, optional)."
msgstr "``read_ahead_size``: 通过首先读取这么多字节来触发文件系统的预读（正整数，可选）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:182
msgid ""
"``use_odirect``: ``true`` or ``false`` (default ``false``) -- bypass the "
"page cache via ``O_DIRECT``."
msgstr ""
"``use_odirect``: ``true`` 或 ``false``（默认 ``false``）-- 通过 ``O_DIRECT`` "
"绕过页面缓存。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:199
msgid "``dax`` -- Device-DAX fixed-slot storage"
msgstr "``dax`` -- 设备-DAX 固定槽存储"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:201
msgid ""
"An L2 adapter that maps Device-DAX paths, such as ``/dev/daxX.X`` and "
"``/dev/daxY.Y``, and stores KV cache objects in fixed-size slots. This "
"adapter is intended for byte-addressable memory devices such as "
"persistent memory or CXL memory."
msgstr "一个 L2 适配器，用于映射 Device-DAX 路径，例如 ``/dev/daxX.X`` 和 ``/dev/daxY.Y``，并在固定大小的槽中存储 KV Cache 对象。该适配器旨在用于字节可寻址内存设备，例如持久内存或 CXL 内存。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:206
msgid ""
"The MP ``dax`` adapter is volatile in this release.  It keeps the key "
"index in server memory and rebuilds an empty index on restart.  Old bytes"
" may remain on the DAX device, but they are unreachable after the LMCache"
" server restarts."
msgstr ""
"在此版本中，MP ``dax`` 适配器是易失性的。它将键索引保存在服务器内存中，并在重启时重建一个空索引。旧字节可能仍然保留在 DAX "
"设备上，但在 LMCache 服务器重启后无法访问。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:210
msgid "**Required fields for the legacy single-device form:**"
msgstr "**遗留单设备表单的必填字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:212
msgid "``device_path``: Path to the mmap-able DAX device or test file."
msgstr "``device_path``: 可映射的 DAX 设备或测试文件的路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:213
msgid "``max_dax_size_gb``: Number of GiB to map from ``device_path``."
msgstr "``max_dax_size_gb``: 从 ``device_path`` 映射的 GiB 数量。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:214
msgid ""
"``slot_bytes``: Fixed slot size in bytes. This must be large enough for "
"one full LMCache chunk because MP memory descriptors do not expose the "
"non-MP full-chunk size."
msgstr ""
"``slot_bytes``: 固定槽大小（以字节为单位）。这必须足够大，以容纳一个完整的 LMCache 块，因为 MP 内存描述符不暴露非 "
"MP 完整块的大小。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:218
msgid "**Required fields for the multi-device form:**"
msgstr "**多设备表单的必填字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:220
msgid ""
"``devices``: List of objects with ``device_path`` and "
"``max_dax_size_gb``. The list may be empty only when ``hotplug_enabled`` "
"is ``true``."
msgstr "``devices``：包含 ``device_path`` 和 ``max_dax_size_gb`` 的对象列表。只有在 ``hotplug_enabled`` 为 ``true`` 时，列表可以为空。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:222
msgid ""
"``slot_bytes``: Fixed slot size in bytes shared by every DAX device in "
"the adapter facade."
msgstr "``slot_bytes``: 适配器外观中每个 DAX 设备共享的固定槽大小（以字节为单位）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:227
msgid ""
"``hotplug_enabled`` (bool, default ``false``): Enables runtime "
"``/reconfigure/dax/status``, ``/reconfigure/dax/add``, "
"``/reconfigure/dax/remove``, and ``/reconfigure/dax/resize``."
msgstr "``hotplug_enabled`` (bool, default ``false``): 启用运行时 ``/reconfigure/dax/status``、``/reconfigure/dax/add``、``/reconfigure/dax/remove`` 和 ``/reconfigure/dax/resize``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:230
msgid "``num_store_workers`` (int, default ``1``): Store worker threads."
msgstr "``num_store_workers`` (int, default ``1``): 存储工作线程。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:231
msgid "``num_lookup_workers`` (int, default ``1``): Lookup worker threads."
msgstr "``num_lookup_workers`` (int, default ``1``): 查找工作线程。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:232
msgid ""
"``num_load_workers`` (int, default ``min(4, os.cpu_count())``): Load "
"worker threads."
msgstr "``num_load_workers`` (int, default ``min(4, os.cpu_count())``): 加载工作线程。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:234
msgid ""
"``persist_enabled`` (bool): Accepted by common L2 config parsing but has "
"no effect for ``dax`` because restart recovery is not implemented."
msgstr "``persist_enabled`` (bool): 被常见的 L2 配置解析接受，但对 ``dax`` 没有影响，因为未实现重启恢复。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:237 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:529
msgid "**Configuration example:**"
msgstr "**配置示例:**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:273
msgid ""
"Runtime management uses JSON bodies because DAX paths contain slashes. "
"See the :doc:`Device-DAX backend guide </kv_cache/storage_backends/dax>` "
"for complete examples. These routes use StorageManager's generic L2 "
"adapter reconfiguration API; the HTTP path selects the backend and "
"operation, the DAX adapter interprets the operation payload, and the same"
" interface can be reused by future adapters such as P2P."
msgstr "运行时管理使用 JSON 主体，因为 DAX 路径包含斜杠。有关完整示例，请参见 :doc:`设备-DAX 后端指南 </kv_cache/storage_backends/dax>`。这些路由使用 StorageManager 的通用 L2 适配器重新配置 API；HTTP 路径选择后端和操作，DAX 适配器解释操作有效负载，未来的适配器如 P2P 也可以重用相同的接口。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:288
msgid "**Current limits:**"
msgstr "**当前限制：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:290
msgid ""
"Runtime hotplug changes only LMCache mappings and metadata. It does not "
"create, destroy, or reconfigure kernel CXL or DAX devices."
msgstr "运行时热插拔仅更改 LMCache 映射和元数据。它不会创建、销毁或重新配置内核 CXL 或 DAX 设备。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:292
msgid "Per-TP partitions and on-device restart metadata are not implemented."
msgstr "每个 TP 的分区和设备重启元数据尚未实现。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:293
msgid ""
"Only single-buffer objects are supported. Multi-tensor objects are "
"rejected."
msgstr "仅支持单缓冲区对象。多张量对象会被拒绝。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:294
msgid ""
"Capacity is slot-based, not payload-byte-based. L2 eviction and usage "
"metrics count occupied slots."
msgstr "容量是基于插槽的，而不是基于有效载荷字节的。L2 逐出和使用指标计算占用的插槽。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:296
msgid ""
"Lookups acquire DAX-side external locks. ``submit_unlock`` releases those"
" locks after load/retrieve completes, making entries evictable again."
msgstr "查找会获取 DAX 侧的外部锁。``submit_unlock`` 在加载/检索完成后释放这些锁，使条目可以再次被逐出。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:298
msgid ""
"Remove ``mode=\"evict\"`` is destructive for the DAX tier. Remove "
"``mode=\"migrate\"`` requires enough capacity on another active DAX "
"device."
msgstr "移除 ``mode=\"evict\"`` 对 DAX 层是破坏性的。移除 ``mode=\"migrate\"`` 需要另一个活动 DAX 设备上有足够的容量。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:302
msgid "``fs_native`` -- Native C++ file-system connector"
msgstr "``fs_native`` -- 原生 C++ 文件系统连接器"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:304
msgid ""
"A file-system L2 adapter backed by the native C++ ``LMCacheFSClient`` "
"wrapped with ``NativeConnectorL2Adapter``.  I/O is dispatched through a "
"C++ worker-thread pool with eventfd-driven completions, giving a true I/O"
" queue depth on a single Python thread."
msgstr ""
"一个由原生 C++ ``LMCacheFSClient`` 支持的文件系统 L2 适配器，封装在 "
"``NativeConnectorL2Adapter`` 中。I/O 通过一个 C++ 工作线程池进行调度，使用 eventfd "
"驱动的完成机制，在单个 Python 线程上提供真实的 I/O 队列深度。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:315
msgid ""
"``num_workers`` (int, default ``4``, > 0): Number of C++ worker threads "
"inside the connector.  This is the real I/O queue depth -- raise to push "
"throughput on filesystems whose aggregate BW exceeds per-stream BW."
msgstr ""
"``num_workers`` (int, default ``4``, > 0): 连接器内部的 C++ 工作线程数量。这是真正的 I/O "
"队列深度——增加此值以提高在总带宽超过每个流带宽的文件系统上的吞吐量。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:319
msgid ""
"``relative_tmp_dir`` (str, default ``\"\"``): Relative sub-directory for "
"temporary files during writes (atomic rename on completion)."
msgstr "``relative_tmp_dir`` (str, default ``\"\"``): 写入期间临时文件的相对子目录（完成时原子重命名）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:321
msgid ""
"``use_odirect`` (bool, default ``false``): Bypass the page cache via "
"``O_DIRECT``.  Required to measure real disk bandwidth.  See alignment "
"caveat below."
msgstr ""
"``use_odirect`` (bool, default ``false``): 通过 ``O_DIRECT`` 绕过页面缓存。 "
"需要测量真实的磁盘带宽。 请参见下面的对齐注意事项。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:324
msgid ""
"``read_ahead_size`` (int, optional): Trigger filesystem readahead by "
"issuing a warm-up read of this many bytes at open time."
msgstr "``read_ahead_size`` (int, optional): 在打开时通过发出此字节数的预热读取来触发文件系统的预读取。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:326
msgid ""
"``max_capacity_gb`` (float, default ``0``): Maximum L2 capacity in GB for"
" client-side usage tracking.  Default ``0`` disables tracking."
msgstr ""
"``max_capacity_gb`` (float, default ``0``): 客户端使用跟踪的最大 L2 容量（以 GB "
"为单位）。默认值 ``0`` 禁用跟踪。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:331
msgid "``O_DIRECT`` has two independent alignment requirements:"
msgstr "``O_DIRECT`` 有两个独立的对齐要求："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:333
#, python-format
msgid ""
"**Length alignment.**  The transfer length must be a multiple of the "
"filesystem's block size.  The connector queries the disk block size at "
"construction time and, on each operation, checks ``len % "
"disk_block_size``.  If the length is **not** a multiple, the connector "
"silently falls back to a buffered open (no ``O_DIRECT``) for that "
"operation -- correctness is preserved but you do not get true direct I/O."
"  To ensure ``O_DIRECT`` is actually used, choose ``--chunk-size`` so "
"that the resulting per-chunk byte size is a multiple of the FS block "
"size.  GPFS and similar parallel filesystems often use large blocks (e.g."
" several MiB)."
msgstr ""
"**长度对齐。**  传输长度必须是文件系统块大小的倍数。连接器在构造时查询磁盘块大小，并在每次操作时检查 ``len % "
"disk_block_size``。如果长度 **不是** 倍数，连接器会默默回退到缓冲打开（不使用 "
"``O_DIRECT``）进行该操作——正确性得以保留，但您无法获得真正的直接 I/O。为了确保实际使用 ``O_DIRECT``，选择 "
"``--chunk-size`` 使得每块的字节大小是文件系统块大小的倍数。GPFS 和类似的并行文件系统通常使用较大的块（例如几个 MiB）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:345
msgid ""
"**Memory-buffer alignment.**  The I/O buffer pointer itself must also be "
"aligned (typically to 4096 bytes on local disks, or to the FS block size "
"on parallel filesystems).  This is controlled by ``--l1-align-bytes`` "
"(default ``4096``) -- raise it to match the FS block size when running on"
" a filesystem with larger blocks.  If the buffer is misaligned, the "
"underlying ``read``/``write`` syscall returns ``EINVAL`` (this is **not**"
" caught by the length-fallback path above and will surface as a runtime "
"error)."
msgstr ""
"**内存缓冲区对齐。** I/O 缓冲区指针本身也必须对齐（通常在本地磁盘上对齐到 4096 字节，或在并行文件系统上对齐到 FS 块大小）。这由"
" ``--l1-align-bytes`` 控制（默认值为 ``4096``）——在使用块较大的文件系统时，将其提高以匹配 FS "
"块大小。如果缓冲区未对齐，底层的 ``read``/``write`` 系统调用将返回 "
"``EINVAL``（这不会被上面的长度回退路径捕获，并将作为运行时错误出现）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:354
msgid ""
"If unsure, start with ``use_odirect: false`` and confirm correctness "
"before enabling ``O_DIRECT``."
msgstr "如果不确定，请先使用 ``use_odirect: false`` 并确认正确性，然后再启用 ``O_DIRECT``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:370
msgid ""
"**Buffer-only mode example.**  L1 acts as a pure write buffer that "
"absorbs the peak burst of in-flight chunks while the C++ worker pool "
"drains them to disk; nothing is retained in L1 once a store completes:"
msgstr ""
"**仅缓冲区模式示例。** L1 充当一个纯写缓冲区，吸收在飞行块的峰值突发，同时 C++ 工作池将它们写入磁盘；一旦存储完成，L1 "
"中不会保留任何内容："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:385
msgid "``raw_block`` -- Raw block device backed persistent storage"
msgstr "``raw_block`` -- 原始块设备支持的持久存储"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:387
msgid ""
"A built-in L2 adapter that stores KV objects in fixed-size slots on a raw"
" block device or pre-sized file using the Rust raw-device I/O bindings. "
"It reuses the existing raw-block metadata checkpoint model and writes "
"directly into the caller-provided load buffers during prefetch."
msgstr ""
"一个内置的 L2 适配器，它使用 Rust 原始设备 I/O 绑定将 KV "
"对象存储在原始块设备或预先大小化的文件的固定大小槽中。它重用现有的原始块元数据检查点模型，并在预取期间直接写入调用者提供的加载缓冲区。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:394
msgid "``device_path``: Raw device path or pre-sized file path."
msgstr "``device_path``: 原始设备路径或预先大小的文件路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:395
msgid ""
"``slot_bytes``: Fixed slot size in bytes. Must be aligned to "
"``block_align``."
msgstr "``slot_bytes``: 固定的槽大小（以字节为单位）。必须与 ``block_align`` 对齐。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:399
msgid ""
"``capacity_bytes``: Optional cap on the usable device bytes. Default "
"``0`` means use the full device/file size."
msgstr "``capacity_bytes``: 可选的可用设备字节上限。默认值 ``0`` 表示使用整个设备/文件大小。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:401
msgid "``use_odirect``: ``true`` or ``false`` (default ``true``)."
msgstr "``use_odirect``: ``true`` 或 ``false``（默认 ``true``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:402
msgid "``block_align``: Device alignment in bytes (default ``4096``)."
msgstr "``block_align``: 设备对齐字节数（默认 ``4096``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:403
msgid "``header_bytes``: Per-slot header reservation (default ``4096``)."
msgstr "``header_bytes``: 每个槽位的头部保留字节数（默认 ``4096``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:404
msgid ""
"``meta_total_bytes``: Reserved metadata checkpoint region (default "
"``256MiB``)."
msgstr "``meta_total_bytes``: 保留的元数据检查点区域（默认 ``256MiB``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:405
msgid ""
"``meta_magic`` / ``meta_version``: Metadata checkpoint identity/version "
"knobs."
msgstr "``meta_magic`` / ``meta_version``: 元数据检查点标识/版本控制。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:406
msgid ""
"``meta_checkpoint_interval_sec`` / ``meta_idle_quiet_ms`` / "
"``meta_enable_periodic`` / ``meta_verify_on_load``: Checkpoint and "
"recovery controls carried over from the legacy raw-block backend."
msgstr ""
"``meta_checkpoint_interval_sec`` / ``meta_idle_quiet_ms`` / "
"``meta_enable_periodic`` / ``meta_verify_on_load``: 从遗留的原始块后端继承的检查点和恢复控制。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:409
msgid ""
"``load_checkpoint_on_init``: Load an existing on-device metadata "
"checkpoint during startup (default ``true``). Set to ``false`` to start "
"with an empty in-memory index instead."
msgstr ""
"``load_checkpoint_on_init``: 在启动时加载现有的设备元数据检查点（默认值为 ``true``）。设置为 "
"``false`` 以使用空的内存索引开始。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:412
msgid "``enable_zero_copy``: Try aligned direct-buffer I/O when possible."
msgstr "``enable_zero_copy``: 尝试在可能的情况下使用对齐的直接缓冲区 I/O。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:413
msgid ""
"``io_engine``: Rust raw-block I/O engine. Valid values are ``\"posix\"`` "
"(default synchronous ``pread``/``pwrite`` path), ``\"io_uring\"`` (direct"
" Rust io_uring syscall path)."
msgstr ""
"``io_engine``: Rust 原始块 I/O 引擎。有效值为 ``\"posix\"``（默认同步 "
"``pread``/``pwrite`` 路径），``\"io_uring\"``（直接 Rust io_uring 系统调用路径）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:416
msgid ""
"``use_uring_cmd``: Enable NVMe passthrough via io_uring command interface"
" for direct device access. Requires ``io_engine=\"io_uring\"`` and NVMe "
"character device node (e.g., ``/dev/ng0n1``)."
msgstr "``use_uring_cmd``: 通过 io_uring 命令接口启用 NVMe 直通以直接访问设备。需要 ``io_engine=\\\"io_uring\\\"`` 和 NVMe 字符设备节点（例如，``/dev/ng0n1``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:419
msgid "``iouring_queue_depth``: Queue depth for ``io_engine=\"io_uring\"``."
msgstr "``iouring_queue_depth``: ``io_engine=\"io_uring\"`` 的队列深度。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:420
msgid ""
"``max_data_transfer_size``: Maximum data transfer size for "
"``use_uring_cmd=true``. Large transfers are split into smaller chunks "
"that fit within device limits."
msgstr "``max_data_transfer_size``: ``use_uring_cmd=true`` 的最大数据传输大小。大数据传输会被拆分成适合设备限制的小块。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:423
msgid ""
"``num_store_workers`` / ``num_lookup_workers`` / ``num_load_workers``: "
"Worker-thread counts for each operation type."
msgstr ""
"``num_store_workers`` / ``num_lookup_workers`` / ``num_load_workers``: "
"每种操作类型的工作线程数量。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:426
msgid "**Notes:**"
msgstr "**注意：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:428
msgid ""
"``raw_block`` is a server-owned MP adapter. It does **not** support per-"
"TP device-path mappings in MP mode."
msgstr "``raw_block`` 是一个由服务器拥有的 MP 适配器。它 **不** 支持 MP 模式下的每个 TP 设备路径映射。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:430
msgid ""
"``raw_block`` remains ``\"type\": \"raw_block\"`` for all supported "
"engines."
msgstr "``raw_block`` 对于所有支持的引擎保持 ``\"type\": \"raw_block\"``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:431
msgid ""
"``raw_block`` owns on-device slot allocation, checkpointing, and recovery"
" through ``RawBlockCore``. Slot reclamation is driven by the "
"shared/global L2 eviction controller or explicit ``delete()`` calls."
msgstr ""
"``raw_block`` 拥有设备上的槽分配、检查点和通过 ``RawBlockCore`` 的恢复。槽回收由共享/全局 L2 "
"逐出控制器或显式的 ``delete()`` 调用驱动。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:434
msgid ""
"If ``use_odirect`` is enabled, the server's ``--l1-align-bytes`` should "
"be at least ``block_align``."
msgstr "如果启用了 ``use_odirect``，则服务器的 ``--l1-align-bytes`` 应至少为 ``block_align``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:436
msgid "``persist_enabled`` must remain ``true`` for this adapter."
msgstr "``persist_enabled`` 必须保持为 ``true`` 以便此适配器正常工作。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:437
msgid ""
"For ``use_uring_cmd=true``, ``device_path`` must use the NVMe character "
"device node (e.g., ``/dev/ng0n1``) instead of the block device node "
"(``/dev/nvme0n1``). The character device provides direct NVMe command "
"passthrough."
msgstr "对于 ``use_uring_cmd=true``，``device_path`` 必须使用 NVMe 字符设备节点（例如，``/dev/ng0n1``），而不是块设备节点（``/dev/nvme0n1``）。字符设备提供直接的 NVMe 命令直通。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:441
msgid "``use_uring_cmd`` requires ``io_engine=\"io_uring\"`` to be set."
msgstr "``use_uring_cmd`` 需要设置 ``io_engine=\"io_uring\"``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:442
msgid ""
"When ``use_uring_cmd=true``, ``use_odirect`` is ignored for NVMe "
"namespace character devices."
msgstr "当 ``use_uring_cmd=true`` 时，NVMe 命名空间字符设备将忽略 ``use_odirect``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:462
msgid "``mooncake_store`` -- Mooncake Store native connector"
msgstr "``mooncake_store`` -- Mooncake Store 原生连接器"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:464
msgid ""
"An L2 adapter backed by the native C++ Mooncake Store connector.  Uses "
"`Mooncake <https://github.com/kvcache-ai/Mooncake>`_ for high-performance"
" distributed KV cache storage with RDMA support."
msgstr ""
"一个由原生 C++ Mooncake Store 连接器支持的 L2 适配器。使用 `Mooncake <https://github.com"
"/kvcache-ai/Mooncake>`_ 进行高性能分布式 KV Cache 存储，并支持 RDMA。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:468
msgid ""
"When Mooncake is configured with ``\"protocol\": \"rdma\"``, LMCache must"
" also have a valid contiguous L1 memory region available.  The "
"distributed storage manager passes this L1 memory descriptor to the "
"adapter factory automatically in MP mode.  If the descriptor is missing "
"or invalid, adapter creation fails with ``ValueError`` instead of "
"silently falling back to a non-RDMA path."
msgstr ""
"当 Mooncake 配置为 ``\"protocol\": \"rdma\"`` 时，LMCache 还必须有一个有效的连续 L1 "
"内存区域可用。分布式存储管理器会在 MP 模式下自动将此 L1 内存描述符传递给适配器工厂。如果描述符缺失或无效，适配器创建将失败并抛出 "
"``ValueError``，而不是默默回退到非 RDMA 路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:474
msgid "**Prerequisites -- Building with Mooncake support:**"
msgstr "**前提条件 -- 构建 Mooncake 支持：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:476
msgid ""
"The Mooncake extension is **not** built by default.  You must explicitly "
"enable it:"
msgstr "Mooncake 扩展**默认情况下**并未构建。您必须显式启用它："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:483
msgid "The ``BUILD_MOONCAKE`` environment variable controls compilation:"
msgstr "``BUILD_MOONCAKE`` 环境变量控制编译："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:485
msgid "``BUILD_MOONCAKE=1``: Enable the Mooncake C++ extension."
msgstr "``BUILD_MOONCAKE=1``：启用 Mooncake C++ 扩展。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:486
msgid ""
"``BUILD_MOONCAKE=0``: Force disable (highest priority), even if "
"``MOONCAKE_INCLUDE_DIR`` is set."
msgstr "``BUILD_MOONCAKE=0``: 强制禁用（最高优先级），即使 ``MOONCAKE_INCLUDE_DIR`` 已设置。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:488
msgid ""
"**Not set**: Falls back to checking ``MOONCAKE_INCLUDE_DIR`` for backward"
" compatibility.  If ``MOONCAKE_INCLUDE_DIR`` is also unset, the extension"
" is skipped."
msgstr ""
"**未设置**：回退到检查 ``MOONCAKE_INCLUDE_DIR`` 以保持向后兼容。如果 "
"``MOONCAKE_INCLUDE_DIR`` 也未设置，则跳过该扩展。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:492
msgid ""
"If the Mooncake headers are not installed in the system include path "
"(e.g., ``/usr/local/include``), you must point to them explicitly:"
msgstr "如果系统的包含路径中没有安装 Mooncake 头文件（例如，``/usr/local/include``），您必须明确指定它们："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:502
msgid "**LMCache-specific fields:**"
msgstr "**LMCache-specific fields:**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:504
msgid ""
"``num_workers``: Number of C++ worker threads for the shared pool "
"(default ``4``, must be > 0)."
msgstr "``num_workers``: 共享池的 C++ 工作线程数量（默认 ``4``，必须大于 0）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:507
msgid ""
"``per_op_workers`` (``dict[str, int]``, optional): A dict mapping lane "
"keys to dedicated worker thread counts.  Supported keys:"
msgstr "``per_op_workers`` (``dict[str, int]``, 可选): 一个将车道键映射到专用工作线程计数的字典。 支持的键:"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:510
msgid "``\"lookup\"`` — threads for ``EXISTS`` operations."
msgstr "``\"lookup\"`` — 用于 ``EXISTS`` 操作的线程。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:511
msgid "``\"retrieve\"`` — threads for ``GET`` / load operations."
msgstr "``\"retrieve\"`` — 处理 ``GET`` / 加载操作的线程。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:512
msgid "``\"store\"`` — threads for ``SET`` / put operations."
msgstr "``\"store\"`` — 处理 ``SET`` / 放置操作的线程。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:513
msgid "``\"delete\"`` — threads for ``DELETE`` operations."
msgstr "``\"delete\"`` — 处理 ``DELETE`` 操作的线程。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:515
msgid ""
"Operations whose lane key is **not** present in the dict use the shared "
"``num_workers`` pool.  There is no requirement to set all keys — you can "
"configure only the lanes that need dedicated pools."
msgstr "在字典中不存在车道键的操作使用共享的 ``num_workers`` 池。没有必要设置所有键 — 您可以仅配置需要专用池的车道。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:519
msgid "**Mooncake fields:**"
msgstr "**Mooncake 字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:521
msgid ""
"All other keys in the JSON config (except ``type``, ``num_workers``, "
"``per_op_workers``, and ``eviction``) are forwarded **as-is** to "
"Mooncake's ``setup_internal(ConfigDict)``.  Refer to the `Mooncake "
"documentation <https://github.com/kvcache-ai/Mooncake>`_ for available "
"setup keys (e.g., ``local_hostname``, ``metadata_server``, "
"``master_server_addr``, ``protocol``, ``rdma_devices``, "
"``global_segment_size``)."
msgstr ""
"JSON 配置中的所有其他键（除了 ``type``, ``num_workers``, ``per_op_workers``, 和 "
"``eviction``）都将 **原样** 转发到 Mooncake 的 "
"``setup_internal(ConfigDict)``。有关可用的设置键（例如 ``local_hostname``, "
"``metadata_server``, ``master_server_addr``, ``protocol``, "
"``rdma_devices``, ``global_segment_size``），请参阅 `Mooncake 文档 "
"<https://github.com/kvcache-ai/Mooncake>`_ 。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:559
msgid ""
"For full Mooncake setup instructions (master service, metadata server, "
"etc.), see `Mooncake <https://github.com/kvcache-ai/Mooncake>`_ ."
msgstr ""
"有关完整的 Mooncake 设置说明（主服务、元数据服务器等），请参见 `Mooncake <https://github.com"
"/kvcache-ai/Mooncake>`_ 。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:562
msgid "**RDMA notes:**"
msgstr "**RDMA 注意事项：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:564
msgid "``protocol: \"rdma\"`` requires a valid LMCache L1 memory descriptor."
msgstr "``protocol: \\\"rdma\\\"`` 需要一个有效的 LMCache L1 内存描述符。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:565
msgid ""
"When using ``protocol: \"rdma\"``, it is recommended to disable lazy L1 "
"allocation with ``--no-l1-use-lazy`` so the L1 buffer is fully allocated "
"before Mooncake registers it."
msgstr ""
"在使用 ``protocol: \\\"rdma\\\"`` 时，建议通过 ``--no-l1-use-lazy`` 禁用延迟 L1 分配，以便在"
" Mooncake 注册之前完全分配 L1 缓冲区。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:568
msgid "``protocol: \"tcp\"`` does not require L1 preregistration."
msgstr "``protocol: \\\"tcp\\\"`` 不需要 L1 预注册。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:569
msgid ""
"If Mooncake RDMA initialization fails at adapter creation time, verify "
"that LMCache L1 memory is enabled and that the descriptor has a non-zero "
"pointer and size."
msgstr "如果 Mooncake RDMA 初始化在适配器创建时失败，请验证 LMCache L1 内存是否已启用，并确保描述符具有非零指针和大小。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:574
msgid "``s3`` -- S3-compatible object store"
msgstr "``s3`` -- S3 兼容对象存储"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:576
msgid ""
"An L2 adapter that stores KV cache objects as S3 objects using the AWS "
"Common Runtime (CRT).  Works with AWS S3, S3 Express One Zone, and any "
"S3-compatible endpoint (MinIO, Ceph RGW, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"一个 L2 适配器，使用 AWS 通用运行时 (CRT) 将 KV Cache 对象存储为 S3 对象。支持 AWS S3、S3 Express "
"One Zone 以及任何 S3 兼容的端点（如 MinIO、Ceph RGW 等）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:582
msgid ""
"``s3_endpoint``: Bucket URL -- either ``\"s3://<bucket>\"`` or the bare "
"host form (used for non-AWS endpoints)."
msgstr "``s3_endpoint``: 存储桶 URL -- 可以是 ``\"s3://<bucket>\"`` 或裸主机形式（用于非 AWS 端点）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:584
msgid "``s3_region``: AWS region string (e.g. ``\"us-west-2\"``)."
msgstr "``s3_region``: AWS 区域字符串（例如 ``\"us-west-2\"``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:588
msgid "``s3_num_io_threads`` (int, default ``64``): Number of CRT I/O threads."
msgstr "``s3_num_io_threads`` (int, default ``64``): CRT I/O 线程的数量。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:589
msgid "``s3_prefer_http2`` (bool, default ``true``): Negotiate HTTP/2 via ALPN."
msgstr "``s3_prefer_http2`` (bool, default ``true``): 通过 ALPN 协商 HTTP/2。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:590
msgid ""
"``s3_enable_s3express`` (bool, default ``false``): Enable S3 Express "
"signing for S3 Express One Zone buckets."
msgstr ""
"``s3_enable_s3express`` (bool, default ``false``): 为 S3 Express 单区桶启用 S3 "
"Express 签名。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:592
msgid ""
"``disable_tls`` (bool, default ``false``): Bypass TLS when pointing at a "
"plain-HTTP endpoint (e.g. a local MinIO)."
msgstr ""
"``disable_tls`` (bool, default ``false``): 在指向普通 HTTP 端点时绕过 TLS（例如，本地 "
"MinIO）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:594
msgid ""
"``aws_access_key_id`` / ``aws_secret_access_key`` (string): Static "
"credentials; omit both to use the AWS default credential provider chain "
"(environment, EC2 instance profile, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"``aws_access_key_id`` / ``aws_secret_access_key`` (字符串): 静态凭证；省略两者以使用 AWS"
" 默认凭证提供程序链（环境、EC2 实例配置文件等）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:597
msgid ""
"``max_capacity_gb`` (float, default ``0.0``): Aggregate capacity used by "
"``get_usage()``.  A value of ``0`` disables aggregate eviction "
"(``usage_fraction == -1.0``)."
msgstr ""
"``max_capacity_gb`` (浮点数，默认 ``0.0``)：``get_usage()`` 使用的总容量。值为 ``0`` "
"将禁用总的逐出（``usage_fraction == -1.0``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:615
msgid "``hfbucket`` -- Hugging Face Buckets"
msgstr "``hfbucket`` -- Hugging Face 存储桶"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:617
msgid ""
"An L2 adapter that stores KV cache objects in a `Hugging Face Bucket "
"<https://huggingface.co/docs/hub/storage-backends>`_ using the "
"``huggingface_hub`` bucket APIs.  Blocking Hub calls run on a bounded "
"thread pool driven by an asyncio loop on a daemon thread, so the L2 "
"controller thread is never blocked on network I/O."
msgstr "一个 L2 适配器，它使用 ``huggingface_hub`` 桶 API 将 KV Cache 对象存储在 `Hugging Face Bucket <https://huggingface.co/docs/hub/storage-backends>`_ 中。阻塞的 Hub 调用在一个由 asyncio 循环驱动的有界线程池上运行在一个守护线程中，因此 L2 控制器线程在网络 I/O 上从不被阻塞。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:623
msgid ""
"Object names are derived from the MP ``ObjectKey`` as "
"``<model>@<kv_rank_hex>@<chunk_hash_hex>[@<cache_salt>]`` and then "
"encoded with the standard HFBucket object-name encoding plus the optional"
" bucket prefix. Because Hugging Face batch writes are not transactional, "
"a store task that partially fails reconciles backend metadata so that any"
" objects that actually landed are still counted for usage accounting and "
"later deletion."
msgstr "对象名称源自 MP ``ObjectKey``，格式为 ``<model>@<kv_rank_hex>@<chunk_hash_hex>[@<cache_salt>]``，然后使用标准的 HFBucket 对象名称编码以及可选的桶前缀进行编码。由于 Hugging Face 批量写入不是事务性的，因此部分失败的存储任务会协调后端元数据，以确保实际存储的对象仍然计入使用量核算和后续删除。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:630
msgid ""
"This is a persistent remote backend best suited to warm and cold KV cache"
" tiers; prefer a lower-latency local adapter for the hottest cache tier."
msgstr "这是一个持久的远程后端，最适合温存和冷存储 KV Cache 层；对于最热的缓存层，建议使用延迟更低的本地适配器。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:635
msgid ""
"``bucket_handle``: Bucket location in the form "
"``hf://buckets/<namespace>/<bucket>[/<prefix>]``."
msgstr "``bucket_handle``: 存储桶位置，格式为 ``hf://buckets/<namespace>/<bucket>[/<prefix>]``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:640
msgid ""
"``token_env`` (string, default ``\"HF_TOKEN\"``): Environment variable "
"used to resolve the Hugging Face access token."
msgstr "``token_env``（字符串，默认 ``\"HF_TOKEN\"``）：用于解析 Hugging Face 访问令牌的环境变量。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:642
msgid ""
"``token`` (string): Direct token fallback used when ``token_env`` is "
"unset."
msgstr "``token`` (string): 当 ``token_env`` 未设置时使用的直接令牌回退。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:643
msgid ""
"``create_bucket_if_missing`` (bool, default ``false``): Create the bucket"
" lazily on the first store instead of requiring it to exist."
msgstr "``create_bucket_if_missing`` (bool, default ``false``): 在第一次存储时懒惰地创建存储桶，而不是要求它必须存在。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:645
msgid ""
"``download_tmp_dir`` (string): Root directory for temporary load "
"downloads."
msgstr "``download_tmp_dir`` (string): 临时加载下载的根目录。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:646
msgid ""
"``metadata_cache_ttl_secs`` (float, default ``30.0``): TTL for the path-"
"size metadata cache that backs lookups and usage accounting."
msgstr "``metadata_cache_ttl_secs`` (float, default ``30.0``): 支持查找和使用计量的路径大小元数据缓存的 TTL。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:648
msgid ""
"``num_workers`` (int, default ``4``): Number of worker threads for "
"blocking Hugging Face Hub API calls."
msgstr "``num_workers`` (整数，默认 ``4``)：用于阻塞 Hugging Face Hub API 调用的工作线程数量。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:650
msgid ""
"``max_capacity_gb`` (float, default ``0.0``): Aggregate capacity used by "
"``get_usage()``.  A value of ``0`` disables aggregate eviction."
msgstr "``max_capacity_gb`` (float, default ``0.0``): ``get_usage()`` 使用的总容量。值为 ``0`` 时禁用总逐出。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:652
msgid ""
"``eviction`` (dict): Optional eviction policy, see "
"``L2AdapterConfigBase``."
msgstr "``eviction`` (字典)：可选的逐出策略，见 ``L2AdapterConfigBase``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:668
msgid "``mock`` -- Mock adapter for testing"
msgstr "``mock`` -- 测试用的模拟适配器"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:670
msgid ""
"Simulates L2 storage with configurable size and bandwidth.  Useful for "
"testing the L2 pipeline without real storage hardware."
msgstr "模拟具有可配置大小和带宽的 L2 存储。对于在没有真实存储硬件的情况下测试 L2 管道非常有用。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:673
msgid "**Fields:**"
msgstr "**字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:675
msgid "``max_size_gb``: Maximum size in GB (> 0)."
msgstr "``max_size_gb``: 最大大小（以 GB 为单位，> 0）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:676
msgid "``mock_bandwidth_gb``: Simulated bandwidth in GB/sec (> 0)."
msgstr "``mock_bandwidth_gb``: 模拟带宽，单位为 GB/秒 (> 0)。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:683
msgid "Multiple Adapters (Cascade)"
msgstr "多个适配器（级联）"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:685
msgid ""
"You can configure multiple L2 adapters by repeating the ``--l2-adapter`` "
"argument.  Adapters are used in the order they are specified.  The "
"``StoreController`` pushes data to all configured adapters, and the "
"``PrefetchController`` queries adapters in order during lookups."
msgstr ""
"您可以通过重复 ``--l2-adapter`` 参数来配置多个 L2 适配器。适配器按指定的顺序使用。``StoreController`` "
"将数据推送到所有配置的适配器，而 ``PrefetchController`` 在查找期间按顺序查询适配器。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:697
msgid "Store and Prefetch Policies"
msgstr "存储和预取策略"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:699
msgid ""
"The **store policy** controls how keys flow from L1 to L2: which adapters"
" receive each key and whether keys are deleted from L1 after a successful"
" L2 store.  The **prefetch policy** controls how keys flow from L2 back "
"to L1: when multiple adapters have the same key, the policy decides which"
" adapter loads it."
msgstr ""
"**存储策略** 控制键从 L1 流向 L2 的方式：哪些适配器接收每个键，以及在成功存储到 L2 后是否从 L1 删除键。 **预取策略** "
"控制键从 L2 流回 L1 的方式：当多个适配器具有相同的键时，该策略决定哪个适配器加载它。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:705
msgid "Select policies via CLI:"
msgstr "通过 CLI 选择策略："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:712
msgid "**Built-in policies:**"
msgstr "**内置策略：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:718 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:751
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:805
msgid "Flag"
msgstr "标志"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:719
msgid "Name"
msgstr "名称"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:720
msgid "Behaviour"
msgstr "行为"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:721 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:724
msgid "``--l2-store-policy``"
msgstr "``--l2-store-policy``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:722 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:730
msgid "``default``"
msgstr "``default``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:723
msgid "Store all keys to all adapters.  Never delete from L1."
msgstr "将所有键存储到所有适配器。永远不要从 L1 中删除。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:725
msgid "``skip_l1``"
msgstr "``skip_l1``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:726
msgid ""
"Buffer-only mode.  Store all keys to all adapters, then **delete them "
"from L1** immediately.  Pair with ``--eviction-policy noop`` to avoid "
"useless LRU overhead."
msgstr ""
"仅缓冲区模式。将所有键存储到所有适配器，然后**立即从 L1 中删除它们**。与 ``--eviction-policy noop`` "
"配对以避免无用的 LRU 开销。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:729 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:733
msgid "``--l2-prefetch-policy``"
msgstr "``--l2-prefetch-policy``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:731
msgid ""
"For each key, pick the first (lowest-indexed) adapter that has it. "
"Prefetched keys are **temporary** (deleted after the reader finishes)."
msgstr "对于每个键，选择第一个（索引最低的）具有该键的适配器。预取的键是**临时的**（在读取器完成后删除）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:734
msgid "``retain``"
msgstr "``retain``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:735
msgid ""
"Same load plan as ``default``, but prefetched keys are **retained** "
"permanently in L1.  Useful when prefetched data is likely reused by "
"subsequent requests (e.g. shared system-prompt chunks)."
msgstr ""
"与 ``default`` 相同的加载计划，但预取的键在 L1 "
"中**永久保留**。当预取的数据可能被后续请求重用时（例如共享的系统提示块），这非常有用。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:740
msgid "Prefetch Concurrency"
msgstr "预取并发性"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:742
msgid ""
"The ``--l2-prefetch-max-in-flight`` flag limits the number of concurrent "
"prefetch requests that the ``PrefetchController`` can have in flight at "
"any time.  A higher value increases L2-to-L1 throughput but also "
"increases L1 memory pressure from in-flight data."
msgstr ""
"``--l2-prefetch-max-in-flight`` 标志限制了 ``PrefetchController`` "
"在任何时候可以同时进行的预取请求数量。更高的值会增加 L2 到 L1 的吞吐量，但也会增加来自在飞数据的 L1 内存压力。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:752 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:806
#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:846
msgid "Default"
msgstr "默认"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:754
msgid "``--l2-prefetch-max-in-flight``"
msgstr "``--l2-prefetch-max-in-flight``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:755
msgid "``8``"
msgstr "``8``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:756
msgid "Maximum number of concurrent prefetch requests."
msgstr "最大并发预取请求数。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:759
msgid "Buffer-Only Mode"
msgstr "仅缓冲区模式"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:761
msgid ""
"When L1 is used purely as a write buffer (all data lives in L2), use "
"``--l2-store-policy skip_l1`` together with ``--eviction-policy noop``. "
"This combination deletes keys from L1 as soon as they are stored to L2 "
"and disables the LRU eviction tracker entirely, reducing memory and CPU "
"overhead."
msgstr ""
"当 L1 仅作为写缓冲区使用（所有数据存储在 L2 中）时，使用 ``--l2-store-policy skip_l1`` 和 "
"``--eviction-policy noop``。此组合会在将键存储到 L2 后立即从 L1 中删除这些键，并完全禁用 LRU "
"逐出跟踪器，从而减少内存和 CPU 开销。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:773
msgid ""
"Policies are extensible -- new policies can be added by creating a file "
"in ``storage_controllers/`` and calling ``register_store_policy()`` or "
"``register_prefetch_policy()`` at import time.  See the design doc "
"``l2_adapters/design_docs/overall.md`` for details."
msgstr ""
"策略是可扩展的 -- 可以通过在 ``storage_controllers/`` 中创建文件并在导入时调用 "
"``register_store_policy()`` 或 ``register_prefetch_policy()`` "
"来添加新策略。有关详细信息，请参见设计文档 ``l2_adapters/design_docs/overall.md``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:779
msgid "Serde (compression / quantization)"
msgstr "序列化（压缩 / 量化）"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:781
msgid ""
"Each adapter can optionally run a **serde** (serializer / deserializer) "
"that transforms data on the way in and out of L2 — e.g. fp8 quantization "
"for disk backends, or encryption for remote adapters. See :doc:`serde` "
"for details and configuration."
msgstr ""
"每个适配器可以选择性地运行一个 **serde**（序列化器/反序列化器），在数据进出 L2 时进行转换——例如，针对磁盘后端的 fp8 "
"量化，或针对远程适配器的加密。有关详细信息和配置，请参见 :doc:`serde`。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:787
msgid "Eviction"
msgstr "逐出"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:789
msgid ""
"LMCache supports eviction at both storage tiers so that each tier can "
"operate within a fixed capacity budget."
msgstr "LMCache 支持在两个存储层次上进行逐出，以便每个层次可以在固定的容量预算内运行。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:793
msgid "L1 Eviction"
msgstr "L1 逐出"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:795
msgid ""
"L1 eviction runs a single background thread that monitors overall L1 "
"memory usage. When usage exceeds ``trigger_watermark``, the eviction "
"policy evicts a fraction of the least-recently-used keys."
msgstr ""
"L1 逐出运行一个后台线程，监控整体 L1 内存使用情况。当使用量超过 ``trigger_watermark`` "
"时，逐出策略会逐出一部分最近最少使用的键。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:799
msgid "**CLI flags:**"
msgstr "**命令行标志：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:808
msgid "``--eviction-policy``"
msgstr "``--eviction-policy``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:809 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:849
msgid "*(required)*"
msgstr "*(必需)*"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:810
msgid "Policy name: ``LRU`` or ``noop``."
msgstr "策略名称：``LRU`` 或 ``noop``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:811
msgid "``--eviction-trigger-watermark``"
msgstr "``--eviction-trigger-watermark``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:812 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:852
msgid "``0.8``"
msgstr "``0.8``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:813
msgid "L1 usage fraction [0, 1] above which eviction is triggered."
msgstr "触发逐出的 L1 使用比例 [0, 1]。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:814
msgid "``--eviction-ratio``"
msgstr "``--eviction-ratio``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:815 ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:855
msgid "``0.2``"
msgstr "``0.2``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:816
msgid "Fraction of currently allocated L1 memory to evict per cycle."
msgstr "每个周期逐出当前分配的 L1 内存的比例。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:818
msgid "**Example:**"
msgstr "**示例：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:827
msgid "L2 Eviction"
msgstr "L2 逐出"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:829
msgid ""
"L2 eviction is **per-adapter** and **opt-in**. Each adapter can "
"independently declare an eviction policy by adding an ``\"eviction\"`` "
"sub-object to its ``--l2-adapter`` JSON spec. Adapters without an "
"``\"eviction\"`` key have no eviction controller."
msgstr ""
"L2 逐出是 **每个适配器** 和 **自愿选择** 的。每个适配器可以通过在其 ``--l2-adapter`` JSON 规范中添加 "
"``\"eviction\"`` 子对象来独立声明逐出策略。没有 ``\"eviction\"`` 键的适配器没有逐出控制器。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:834
msgid ""
"When L2 eviction is enabled for an adapter, a dedicated background thread"
" monitors that adapter's ``get_usage()`` value. Once usage exceeds "
"``trigger_watermark``, the policy evicts keys until usage drops by "
"``eviction_ratio``."
msgstr ""
"当为适配器启用 L2 逐出时，一个专用的后台线程会监视该适配器的 ``get_usage()`` 值。一旦使用量超过 "
"``trigger_watermark``，该策略将逐出键，直到使用量降低到 ``eviction_ratio``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:839
msgid "**``\"eviction\"`` sub-object fields:**"
msgstr "**``\"eviction\"`` 子对象字段:**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:845
msgid "Field"
msgstr "字段"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:848
msgid "``eviction_policy``"
msgstr "``eviction_policy``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:850
msgid "Policy name: ``\"LRU\"`` or ``\"noop\"``."
msgstr "策略名称：``\"LRU\"`` 或 ``\"noop\"``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:851
msgid "``trigger_watermark``"
msgstr "``trigger_watermark``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:853
msgid "Adapter usage fraction [0, 1] above which eviction is triggered."
msgstr "触发逐出的适配器使用比例 [0, 1]。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:854
msgid "``eviction_ratio``"
msgstr "``eviction_ratio``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:856
msgid "Fraction of used capacity to evict per cycle."
msgstr "每个周期逐出的已用容量的比例。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:858
msgid "**Example — nixl_store with LRU eviction:**"
msgstr "**示例 — 使用 LRU 逐出的 nixl_store:**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:874
msgid "**Adapter support:**"
msgstr "**适配器支持：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:880
msgid "Adapter"
msgstr "适配器"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:881
msgid "L2 Eviction Support"
msgstr "L2 逐出支持"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:882
msgid "``nixl_store``"
msgstr "``nixl_store``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:883
msgid ""
"Full support. ``delete`` frees pool slots; pinned keys (in-flight loads) "
"are skipped and retried on the next cycle."
msgstr "完全支持。``delete`` 释放池槽；固定键（正在进行的加载）会被跳过，并在下一个周期重试。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:885
msgid "``nixl_store_dynamic``"
msgstr "``nixl_store_dynamic``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:886
msgid ""
"Full support. ``delete`` removes data files from disk; pinned keys are "
"skipped. ``get_usage`` is byte-based (``_total_bytes / "
"max_capacity_bytes``)."
msgstr ""
"完全支持。``delete`` 从磁盘中删除数据文件；被固定的键会被跳过。``get_usage`` 是基于字节的 (``_total_bytes"
" / max_capacity_bytes``)。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:889
msgid "``mock``"
msgstr "``mock``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:890
msgid ""
"Full support. Useful for testing eviction behaviour without real storage "
"hardware."
msgstr "完全支持。对于测试逐出行为而无需真实存储硬件非常有用。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:892
msgid "``raw_block``"
msgstr "``raw_block``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:893
msgid ""
"Full shared/global eviction support. ``delete`` recycles raw-block slots;"
" locked entries are skipped and retried on the next cycle."
msgstr "完全支持共享/全局逐出。``delete`` 回收原始块槽；被锁定的条目会被跳过，并在下一个周期重试。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:895
msgid "``s3``"
msgstr "``s3``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:896
msgid ""
"``delete`` removes objects from the bucket and frees aggregate byte "
"accounting. ``get_usage`` reports ``usage_fraction == -1.0`` when "
"``max_capacity_gb`` is ``0`` (disabled); set a non-zero "
"``max_capacity_gb`` to enable the watermark-triggered eviction "
"controller."
msgstr ""
"``delete`` 从存储桶中删除对象并释放聚合字节计数。当 ``max_capacity_gb`` 为 "
"``0``（禁用）时，``get_usage`` 报告 ``usage_fraction == -1.0``；设置非零的 "
"``max_capacity_gb`` 以启用基于水印的逐出控制器。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:901
msgid "``hfbucket``"
msgstr "``hfbucket``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:902
msgid ""
"``delete`` removes objects from the bucket and frees aggregate byte "
"accounting. ``get_usage`` reports ``usage_fraction == -1.0`` when "
"``max_capacity_gb`` is ``0`` (disabled); set a non-zero "
"``max_capacity_gb`` to enable the watermark-triggered eviction "
"controller. Locked keys (in-flight loads) are skipped."
msgstr "``delete`` 从桶中移除对象并释放聚合字节计数。当 ``max_capacity_gb`` 为 ``0``（禁用）时，``get_usage`` 报告 ``usage_fraction == -1.0``；设置非零的 ``max_capacity_gb`` 以启用基于水印的逐出控制器。被锁定的键（正在加载的）会被跳过。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:907
msgid "``dax``"
msgstr "``dax``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:908
msgid ""
"Full support. ``delete`` removes unlocked keys from the in-memory index "
"immediately and recycles fixed slots once active read borrows drain. "
"Usage is slot-based."
msgstr "完全支持。``delete`` 会立即从内存索引中移除未锁定的键，并在活动读取借用耗尽后回收固定槽。使用基于槽的方式。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:911
msgid "``mooncake_store``"
msgstr "``mooncake_store``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:912
msgid "No eviction support (native connector adapter)."
msgstr "不支持逐出（原生连接器适配器）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:913
msgid "``fs``"
msgstr "``fs``"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:914
msgid "No eviction support (``delete`` and ``get_usage`` are no-ops)."
msgstr "不支持逐出（``delete`` 和 ``get_usage`` 是无操作）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:915
msgid "native connectors"
msgstr "原生连接器"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:916
msgid "No eviction support."
msgstr "不支持逐出。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:920
msgid ""
"Each L2 adapter instance gets its own independent eviction controller and"
" policy.  Two adapters of the same type can have different watermarks or "
"policies."
msgstr "每个 L2 适配器实例都有自己独立的逐出控制器和策略。两个相同类型的适配器可以有不同的水位线或策略。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:925
msgid "Combined L1 + L2 Eviction Example"
msgstr "L1 + L2 逐出示例"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:945
msgid "In this setup:"
msgstr "在此设置中："

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:947
#, python-format
msgid ""
"L1 evicts from memory when it is 80 % full, reclaiming 20 % of allocated "
"memory per cycle."
msgstr "当 L1 的内存使用达到 80% 时，它会逐出内存，每个周期回收 20% 的分配内存。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:949
#, python-format
msgid ""
"L2 (NIXL/GDS) evicts from the storage pool when 90 % of pool slots are "
"occupied, reclaiming 10 % per cycle."
msgstr "L2 (NIXL/GDS) 在存储池占用 90% 的槽位时进行逐出，每个周期回收 10%。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage.rst:951
msgid ""
"Both tiers use independent LRU policies, so each evicts its own least-"
"recently-used keys."
msgstr "两个层次使用独立的 LRU 策略，因此每个层次逐出其自身最近最少使用的键。"

